post_text:
Fantastic day serving meals with staff to the wonderful kids of Beardsley. Lots of friendly faces and appreciation for the breakfast and lunch provided. Over 600 meals served from this location.

The number one comment was "When can the kids go back, parents are already tired"

Hang in there families we will be back to do it again tomorrow and the many days after. Please tell your friends!!

To help reduce stress and anxiety some families may be feeling, the Beardsley School District will continue to provide nutritious meals to all children 2-18.
Meals served Monday-Friday from 10:30am-12:30pm at any school site. Get yours.
